  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5171257/" class="title-link">用故事讲述观念</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5171257"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ygy8245/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1042441-29.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ygy8245/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">思郁</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-11-16"
      class="main-meta">2011-11-16 01:24:11</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5171257_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本雅明在那篇流传甚广的《讲故事的人》中提到了很多因素，导致“讲故事”这一古老的手艺活的衰落：经验的贬值、信息大于报道、小说的勃兴、远行之人愈来愈少等等。杨照在《故事照亮未来》中敏锐地捕捉到了本雅明的思想精髓：故事消失，其实是因为听故事的人不再好奇，也就是，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5171257/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">23有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5171257_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5171257_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5128557">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5128557/" class="title-link">故事是对生活最好的比喻</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5128557"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/WOSHIFANG/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1867012-23.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/WOSHIFANG/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">正在输入</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-10-11"
      class="main-meta">2011-10-11 21:33:14</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5128557_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      我总认为，看一本书非常讲究时间、地点。我床的左边就放着《马克思主义哲学》，失眠时认真阅读，期盼一觉睡到大天亮；右边放着《金瓶梅》，愿晚上春梦了无痕。而这本书一时还真不知道放哪，厕所已被刘原的《流亡三部曲》霸占，就算过段时间也不会更替，杨照的书是好书，但...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
